      "message": "Maybe the right thing to say is something like \"The policy schema will be installed automatically as part of the db setup - see Using Policy DB Migrator`_. for more information\"\nThis isn't such a big change as this used to be done in the java code in previous releases.\nWe have still been running steps 3 - 6 as part of our testing.\nI think it's OK to keep them if you want to start with a clean install.\nIf you want to upgrade and preserve you existing data then we'll need to make some changes here.",
